1.1.4.name: wordpress/gugl
1.1.4.description:
This plugin can capture a query string when the visitor comes to your Site from Google Results Page. Then you can show your visitor button with prepared text and search phrase to get high CTR.

There is 8 default Color Schemes for button

  • Grey
  • Green
  • Blue
  • Red
  • Orange
  • White
  • Purple
  • Pink

You can also

  • Execute plugin in the Test mode
  • Use atribute target="_blank"
  • Define your own Color Scheme for button with CSS

Languages

  • English
  • Polish

To Do

  • Widget
  • Pro Version with automatically generated links for different phrases

If you like this plugin, please give me some sunshine. Don't forget to review it!
